### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### =====================================
### Get Products - Default (page 1, limit 10)
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist


### =====================================
### Get Products - Page 1
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=1&limit=1


### =====================================
### Get Products - Page 2
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=2&limit=10


### =====================================
### Get Products - Custom Limit
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=1&limit=20


### =====================================
### Get Products - Large Page
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=5&limit=20


### =====================================
### Invalid Page (edge case test)
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=0&limit=10


### =====================================
### Invalid Limit (edge case test)
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=1&limit=500


### =====================================
### With Sorting (if implemented)
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=1&limit=10&sort=price_desc


### =====================================
### With Filtering (if implemented)
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=1&limit=10&minPrice=10000


### =====================================
### Combined (Pagination + Filter + Sort)
### =====================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/productlist?page=2&limit=10&minPrice=20000&sort=price_asc